## Edge Cases

1. **--preset and --min-score together**: clap enforces mutual exclusion
2. **Config file preset**: Can be overridden by CLI flag
3. **Invalid preset name**: clap provides helpful error with valid options
4. **Case sensitivity**: ValueEnum handles case-insensitively

